This is how to generate_integers of a and b:
  Remember that start is min of a and b
  Remember that finish is max of a and b
  Remember that result is []
  Remember that current is start
  Do this sum of diff of finish and start and 1 times:
    When remainder of current and 2 is 0, then:
      Add result to current
    End when
    Increase current
  End do
  The answer is result
